snippet.title: Mathematics I #5 - VC4000
snippet.description: Playing around on a few different challenges on this classic calculus quiz. The layout is adopted to fit young kids, and promote logical calculation. The time limits will challenge adults aswell. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/01/mathematics-i-5-vc-4000.html
